nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 185 is the 163rd issue of the Star Wars Insider magazine and the ninety-third issue published by Titan Magazines. It was published on November 6, 2018.

News, interviews, and the latest Star Wars merchandise and publishing! Take a tour of Hoth as we explore shooting locations in Finse, Norway! Discover the hidden treasures of Rancho Obi-Wan, the "Smithsonian of Star Wars"! And as Darth Maul returns, we snag an exclusive interview with actor Ray Park!
